        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>5. Accuracy of Materials</h2>
            <p>The materials appearing on Meridian's website could include technical, typographical, or photographic errors. Meridian does not warrant that any of the materials on its website are accurate, complete, or current. Meridian may make changes to the materials contained on its website at any time without notice.</p>
        </section>

